description: TypeScript type definitions for the jQuery library version 1.10.x / 2.0.x, including interfaces for AJAX settings, jQuery objects, events, and static methods.

classes.name: JQueryAjaxSettings
classes.description: Interface defining settings for AJAX requests in jQuery.

classes.name: JQueryXHR
classes.description: Interface extending XMLHttpRequest with additional jQuery-specific methods.

classes.name: JQueryCallback
classes.description: Interface for jQuery callback list objects.

classes.name: JQueryGenericPromise
classes.description: Interface for jQuery promises with generic type support.

classes.name: JQueryPromise
classes.description: Interface for jQuery promise objects with callback methods.

classes.name: JQueryDeferred
classes.description: Interface for jQuery deferred objects, extending promises with resolve/reject capabilities.

classes.name: BaseJQueryEventObject
classes.description: Interface representing the jQuery extension of the W3C Event object.

classes.name: JQueryEventObject
classes.description: Composite interface for various jQuery event objects.

classes.name: JQueryParam
classes.description: Function interface for serializing objects into query strings.

classes.name: JQueryEventConstructor
classes.description: Interface for constructing jQuery event objects.

classes.name: JQueryEasing
classes.description: Interface for easing functions used in animations.

classes.name: JQueryStatic
classes.description: Static interface representing the jQuery namespace with all static methods and properties.
